AUTHORIZING A USERID FOR DASD 'ADMIN' AUTHORITY ON SYSE
(IBM VANILLA SYSTEM)

SET GENERIC COMMAND AND GENERIC PROFILE PROCESSING FOR FACILITY CLASS

    FROM THE RACF PRIMARY SELECTION PANEL, SPECIFY SYSTEM OPTIONS.

       THEN SELECT CLASS OPTIONS
         <ENTER>
            SPECIFY GENERIC  YES
            SPECIFY GENERIC COMMANDS YES
            SPECIFY YES FOR SPECIFIC CLASS
         <ENTER>
                    SPECIFY FACILITY UNDER CLASS
                    SPECIFY YES UNDER GENERIC
                    SPECIFY YES UNDER GENERIC COMMANDS
         <ENTER>
    FROM THE RACF PRIMARY SELECTION PANEL, SPECIFY GENERAL RESOURCE PROFILES
      SPECIFY ADD
         <ENTER>
         SPECIFY FACILITY FOR CLASS
         SPECIFY STGADMIN.ADR.** FOR PROFILE
         <ENTER>
         SPECIFY YES TO ADD OPTIONAL INFO (ACCESS LIST)
         <ENTER>
         SPECIFY USERS/GROUPS IN ACCESS LIST
    FROM THE RACF PRIMARY SELECTION PANEL, SPECIFY SYSTEM OPTIONS.
    SPECIFY REFRESH
         <ENTER>
     YES FOR PROGRAM TABLES
     YES FOR SPECIFIC CLASSES
         <ENTER>
     SPECIFY FACILITY UNDER CLASS
     SPECIFY YES UNDER GENERIC
     SPECIFY YES UNDER RACLIST
         <ENTER>

(BACK TO PRIMARY MENU)
RELOG BACK ON
